entry.string:
set +e
pipx install safety || pip install --user safety safety check --full-report --output ${REPORTS_DIR}/owasp/safety-${TIMESTAMP}.json || true
cd frontend npm audit --json > ../${REPORTS_DIR}/owasp/npm-audit-${TIMESTAMP}.json || true cd ..
set -e

trivy image --scanners vuln --skip-db-update --no-progress --format json --output ${REPORTS_DIR}/trivy/backend-${TIMESTAMP}.json ${DOCKER_HUB_USER}/backend:${IMAGE_TAG} || true
trivy image --scanners vuln --skip-db-update --no-progress --format json --output ${REPORTS_DIR}/trivy/frontend-${TIMESTAMP}.json ${DOCKER_HUB_USER}/frontend:${IMAGE_TAG} || true
